narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Again, there are better sections out there that are helpful. That may be the reason why this was the only class that had like 7 students in it. Shop around elsewhere

If you are good at math, its definitely a manageable course. Don't expect to have a helpful and effective teacher. Be prepared to learn most of the subjects in the textbook, which is actually very easy to understand.
